originalText.text: Awesome doctor! I really can’t begin to explain how good my experience was. He was very thorough and explained everything to me. I only go to doctors once a year and he made me feel assured that I was caught up with everything. He followed up with me about my blood tests and went one-by-one through each test with me and explained what things I had to do to improve my numbers. Really excellent experience.
